sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Caller
  participant S as storageService
  participant O as Overlay (staged ops)
  participant P as Provider
  participant EV as EventPublisher port

  C->>S: transaction(fn)
  Note over S: acquire write mutex (atomic read-modify-write)
  S->>O: create empty overlay + op list
  loop fn(tx) stages operations
    C->>S: tx.get / put / update / delete
    S->>O: read-your-writes (overlay → provider), stage put/del + pending event
    Note over S: tx.transaction() → TransactionError (nested guard)
  end
  alt fn resolves
    S->>P: writeBatch(ops)  (atomic commit)
    P-->>S: ok
    S->>S: apply cache + record metrics
    S->>EV: StorageCreated/Updated/Deleted (per op)
    S->>EV: TransactionCommitted
    S-->>C: result
  else fn throws
    Note over S: nothing was written → automatic rollback
    S->>EV: TransactionRolledBack
    S-->>C: rethrow error
  end
  Note over S: release write mutex
